427	## Success Criteria
428	
429	- [ ] Tests written BEFORE implementation (RED phase)
430	- [ ] All tests fail initially (verify RED)
431	- [ ] Shared mock factories used (no manual test data, no inline objects)
432	- [ ] 100% coverage (lines, branches, functions, statements)
433	- [ ] Happy path tested
434	- [ ] Error cases tested
435	- [ ] Edge cases tested
436	- [ ] No `as any` type casting (NEVER)
437	- [ ] DI wiring uses `as never` (not `as unknown as ConstructorParameters<...>`)
438	- [ ] SERVICE_INVENTORY.md updated for new factories
439	- [ ] BEADS task closed with coverage report
